data.description: Beautiful all brick ranch on the end of a cul-de-sac,  4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, knotty pine floors in living room, new LVT tile in bathrooms, owners suite and secondary bedroom, oversized 4th bedroom makes a nice secondary owners suite.  Enjoy the evenings out by the fire pit, fenced back yard is nice and  flat  ideal for a swimming pool.  Location is convenient to schools, highway access and shopping!
